        "subject": "Your Gym subscription will be ending soon",
        "message": "=<!DOCTYPE html> <html> <head>   <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">   <title>Gym Subscription Reminder</title> </head> <body style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;\">    <p>Dear {{ $json.fields['Full Name'] }},</p>    <p>This is a friendly reminder that your <strong>Gym Spec</strong> subscription is approaching its expiration date.</p>    <p>     To ensure uninterrupted access to our facilities and services, kindly take a moment to review and update your subscription details. You can manage your subscription by logging into your account and confirming your <strong>start date</strong> and <strong>end date</strong> to reflect your desired renewal period. </p>    <p><strong>Instructions:</strong></p>   <ol>     <li>Log in to your Gym Spec account.</li> <li>Navigate to the subscription or membership section.</li> Set or update your <strong>start date</strong> and <strong>end date</strong> accordingly.</li> Confirm your changes to complete the renewal process.</li>   </ol>    <p>     If you need any assistance or encounter any issues while updating your subscription, our support team is available to guide you.   </p>    <p>     We value your commitment to your fitness journey and look forward to continuing to support your progress. </p>    <p>Warm regards,<br>   <strong>Gym Spec Team</strong></p>  </body> </html>",
